The paper proposes a generative model for learning from demonstrations and inferring the underlying structure of observed behavior. This involves reasoning about latent features and policies for decision making. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.RO (Robotics).
